---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Operational Systems — Wychwood Partners" description="Install an operating system that turns strategy into execution without bureaucracy.">
  <main class="shell py-14">
    <h1>Operational systems</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      A practical operating model: clear ownership, decision rights, metrics, and routines that keep teams aligned and moving.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">What it includes</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Operating model + accountability</li>
          <li>• Metrics hierarchy (team → exec → board)</li>
          <li>• Decision rights + escalation paths</li>
          <li>• Weekly execution routines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">When it’s needed</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Missed commitments</li>
          <li>• Conflicting priorities</li>
          <li>• Slow decisions</li>
          <li>• “Founder bottleneck”</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Outcomes</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Clear ownership</li>
          <li>• Faster decisions</li>
          <li>• Predictable delivery</li>
          <li>• Reduced chaos</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 card p-8">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Want to assess your operating system?</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">In 30 minutes we’ll identify where rhythm, metrics, and accountability are breaking down.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-5 inline-flex rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] bg-[rgb(var(--brand-anchor))] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:opacity-95">Book a call</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
